Advantages of Arrays ✅
Advantage	Description
Easy Data Storage	Store many values together
Fast Access	Access using index
Dynamic Size	Can grow/shrink
Powerful Methods	Many built-in functions
Easy Iteration	Simple looping
Disadvantages of Arrays ❌
Disadvantage	Description
Index Management	Need to remember indexes
Memory Usage	Large arrays use more memory
Complex Operations	Some operations are slower
Difference Between Array and Object ⚔️
Array	Object
Ordered collection	Key-value pairs
Uses indexes	Uses keys
Best for lists	Best for structured data
Array Example
